    <string name="home_title">Defender Overlay</string>
    <string name="home_intro">Scams keep changing, but warning signs remain similar. Use this guide before sharing money, OTP, passwords, or personal details.</string>
    <string name="home_prevention_title">How To Avoid Scams</string>
    <string name="home_prevention_body">1) Slow down when messages pressure you to act immediately.\n\n2) Verify identity using official channels, never links sent in chats.\n\n3) Check links carefully for misspellings, unusual domains, and shorteners.\n\n4) Never share OTP, PIN, card CVV, or full bank credentials.\n\n5) Treat "refund", "prize", and "account suspension" messages as high risk until verified.\n\n6) When in doubt, stop and ask a trusted person before continuing.</string>
